dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Outagamie County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Outagamie_Hydro_2018.gdb. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are NOutagamie_Hydro_2018_LineN and NOutagamie_Hydro_2018_PolyN. [This is an line feature class identifying the location of all non-navigable and navigable water within Outagamie County. It is a county-wide file including all USGS designated navigable waterways and all non-navigable waterways.This is a polygon feature class that corresponds with navigable streams within Outagamie County. This feature class represents the larger areas of the Navigable Streams.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
